<mxfile host="app.diagrams.net" agent="Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/136.0.0.0 Safari/537.36" version="27.0.6" scale="1" border="0"> <diagram name="Trang-1" id="0vwXOSPtjXcxz2av8c1w"> <mxGraphModel dx="2492" dy="1952" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="827" pageHeight="1169" math="0" shadow="0"> <root> <mxCell id="0" /> <mxCell id="1" parent="0" /> <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{"data":"@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

' Actors
actor Guest as G
actor Member as M
actor Coach as C
actor Admin as A
actor \" <<system>>\nHệ thống cấp huy hiệu\" as Sys

' Generalization
G <|-- M
M <|-- C
C <|-- A

' Boundary
package \"Cai Thuốc Lá Online System\" {

 ' Guest Use Cases
 usecase \"Xem trang chủ\" as UC_Home
 usecase \"Sử dụng công cụ đánh giá mức độ nghiện\" as UC_AssessAddiction
 usecase \"Sử dụng công cụ tính chi phí\" as UC_CostCalc
 usecase \"Xem tài liệu hướng dẫn\" as UC_ViewGuide
 usecase \"Đăng ký tài khoản, gói phí\" as UC_Register
 usecase \"Blog (chỉ đọc)\" as UC_BlogGuest
 usecase \"Forum (chỉ đọc)\" as UC_ForumGuest

 ' Member Use Cases
 usecase \"Quản lý hồ sơ cá nhân\" as UC_ManageProfile
 usecase \"Ghi nhận tình trạng hút thuốc hiện tại\" as UC_RecordSmoking
 usecase \"Tạo, lưu và quản lý kế hoạch cai thuốc\" as UC_ManagePlan
 usecase \"Theo dõi tiến trình cai thuốc\" as UC_TrackProgress
 usecase \"Nhắc nhở & động viên định kỳ\" as UC_ReminderMotivation
 usecase \"Chia sẻ thành tích & tương tác cộng đồng\" as UC_ShareCommunity
 usecase \"Blog\" as UC_BlogMember
 usecase \"Forum\" as UC_ForumMember
 usecase \"Chat & Video Call với Coach\" as UC_ChatCoach
 usecase \"Đánh giá & feedback Coach\" as UC_FeedbackCoach
 usecase \"Dashboard cá nhân\" as UC_Dashboard
 usecase \"A.I. Tư vấn cá nhân hóa\" as UC_AIConsult

 ' Coach Use Cases
 usecase \"Xem danh sách thành viên\" as UC_ViewMembers
 usecase \"Tư vấn & hỗ trợ\" as UC_Advise
 usecase \"Xem báo cáo tiến độ & đánh giá\" as UC_ViewReports
 usecase \"Blog\" as UC_BlogCoach
 usecase \"Forum\" as UC_ForumCoach

 ' Admin Use Cases
 usecase \"Quản lý tài khoản & phân quyền\" as UC_ManageUsers
 usecase \"Quản lý nội dung & gói thành viên\" as UC_ManageContent
 usecase \"Quản lý dịch vụ tin nhắn\" as UC_ManageMessaging
 usecase \"Quản lý rating & feedback\" as UC_ManageFeedback
 usecase \"Dashboard & Report\" as UC_AdminDashboard
 usecase \"Bảo mật & giám sát hệ thống\" as UC_Security
 usecase \"Quản lý nhóm thành viên\" as UC_ManageGroups

 ' System Use Case
 usecase \"Cấp huy hiệu thành tích\" as UC_AwardBadge

}

' Associations Guest
G -- UC_Home
G -- UC_AssessAddiction
G -- UC_CostCalc
G -- UC_ViewGuide
G -- UC_Register
G -- UC_BlogGuest
G -- UC_ForumGuest

' Associations Member
M -- UC_ManageProfile
M -- UC_RecordSmoking
M -- UC_ManagePlan
M -- UC_TrackProgress
M -- UC_ReminderMotivation
M -- UC_ShareCommunity
M -- UC_BlogMember
M -- UC_ForumMember
M -- UC_ChatCoach
M -- UC_FeedbackCoach
M -- UC_Dashboard
M -- UC_AIConsult

' Associations Coach
C -- UC_ViewMembers
C -- UC_Advise
C -- UC_ViewReports
C -- UC_BlogCoach
C -- UC_ForumCoach

' Associations Admin
A -- UC_ManageUsers
A -- UC_ManageContent
A -- UC_ManageMessaging
A -- UC_ManageFeedback
A -- UC_AdminDashboard
A -- UC_Security
A -- UC_ManageGroups

' Associations System
Sys -- UC_AwardBadge

' Include relationships
UC_RecordSmoking ..> UC_ManageProfile : <<include>>
UC_TrackProgress ..> UC_RecordSmoking : <<include>>
UC_AIConsult ..> UC_TrackProgress : <<include>>
UC_Dashboard ..> UC_TrackProgress : <<include>>
UC_Dashboard ..> UC_AwardBadge : <<include>>

' Extend relationships
UC_AssessAddiction <|.. UC_Register : <<extend>> [if not logged in]
UC_ShareCommunity <|.. UC_AwardBadge : <<extend>> [if có huy hiệu]
UC_FeedbackCoach <|.. UC_ChatCoach : <<extend>> [if phiên tư vấn kết thúc]
UC_ReminderMotivation <|.. UC_TrackProgress : <<extend>> [if cần động viên]
UC_TrackProgress <|.. UC_AwardBadge : <<extend>> [if đạt thành tích]

@enduml
